## Summary
This documentation details the User Privacy API, which enables programmatic deletion of user data across Amplitude projects to comply with privacy regulations like GDPR and CCPA, including features for batch deletion requests, organization-wide deletions, and job status monitoring with specific rate limits and scheduling considerations.

